1979;;Ida Makes a Movie;;Canadian;;Kit Hood, Linda Schuyler;;Zoe Newman;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ida_Makes_a_Movie;;The National Film Board of Canada is sponsoring a movie festival. Ida Lucas is a nine-year-old girl who decides to make a movie about the environment (specifically garbage), and enter it into the festival. The judges, thinking the film is about war, accept Ida's film into the festival finals.